~ PHI ~
Creation and decay.
Watch these bold, organic patterns build up and etch away over time.

This visualisation uses the Golden Ratio, emerging from randomness, to determine the colour, positioning and intensity of the painted shapes and lines.

Click and hold the mouse for a burst of fresh colour. Refresh the page for a different tone. Let it run and run, for a beautiful display.

Golden Ratio: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Golden_ratio
Source code: http://github.com/premasagar/js1k/
